            . I live in Mitchell-street, St. Luke's. I was in Chiswell-street, and saw the prisoner take the handkerchief out of Mr. Ball's right hand coat pocket. Mr. Ball turned round, and seized him, and asked me to assist in taking him to the watch-house. There was another person near him.</p>
